                        reductions by treaty, autonomous duties to go into effect in 1906, and
                        reductions granted to certain European countries on forty-six articles of
                        imports, expressed in American currency per 100 kilograms</hi> (<hi
                        rend="italic">220.4 pounds</hi>).</p>
